1 Previos versions

  • GxA results version 1 @ 2017-09-19
  • Current version (this document)

2 Description of results

  • Outcomes of interest included 6 continious traits
    • 1 binary trait was not considered, as mixed models take much more time.
  • We tested for association only 37,000 clean and long ancestry segements.
  • We fited linear mixed models (LMM)
    • No PCs were included as covariates.

2.1 Significannt thresholds

2.1.1 Bonferroni threshold

0.05 / 37e3
[1] 1.351351e-06
  • None of association signals per traits survives the multiple-testing correction.
  • The Bonferroni threshold is conservative for our (corelated) tests.

trait ver formula
FEV1_FVC_utah 9 FEV1_FVC_utah ~ Age_Enroll + Age_Enroll2 + gender + Duration_Smoking + log_CigPerDaySmokAvg + SmokCigNow + SmokCigNow0_15 + acs_global + (0 + dummy(SmokCigNow0_15Rev)|rsid1) + (0 + dummy(SmokCigNowRev)|rsid2) + (1|ccenter)
FEV1pp_utah 9 FEV1pp_utah ~ Age_Enroll + gender + Duration_Smoking + log_CigPerDaySmokAvg + SmokCigarNow + SmokCigNow + SmokCigNow0_15 + acs_global + (0 + dummy(SmokCigNow0_15Rev)|rsid1) + (0 + dummy(SmokCigNowRev)|rsid2) + (1|ccenter)

4 Single-trait association

  • Figure: qq-plot of p-values coming from linear mixed model
  • Table of the top signals was produced as follows:
    1. filter out associations with p-values above 0.001
    2. join results across traits
    3. filter top results
      • create a summary table with the lowest p-value across traits
      • take only top 5 associations from each chromosome
      • recored acs. segments remained
    4. filter top results by those acs. segments remained
    5. note that some p-values can be lost, but the highest p-values per each chromosome are shown
  • Gene annotation is performed withing 100,000b window.

5.2 Correlation among z-scores

5.2.1 Protocol

  1. Standartize z_i
  2. Filter z_i by threshold (default value 2)
  3. Run ML optimization (R function optim, method Brent) for each pairs of z_i and z_j separately
    • the likelihood is derived for truncated MVN (Hugos R code)
